text: Congress should immediately take up the Securing America’s Future Elections Act and ensure that American elections are fair and free. #SAFEAct

Last year, I introduced the Securing America’s Future Elections Act, legislation that would safeguard our elections from future foreign cyber-attacks & interference by permanently classifying the integrity & security of our elections as a key component of critical infrastructure.

Robert Mueller charged 13 Russians with interfering in the 2016 election the same week leading intel officials warned that Russia plans to meddle in the 2018 elections.
